<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge"/>
  <title>Sua operação em conformidade com o Guide Renault 2026</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Manrope:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
  <style>
    /* Reset básico para e-mails */
    body, table, td { margin:0; padding:0; border:0; }
    body { background-color:#C7CDE9; font-family: 'Manrope', Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; }
    img { border:0; display:block; outline:none; text-decoration:none; max-width:100%; }
    table { border-collapse: collapse; mso-table-lspace:0pt; mso-table-rspace:0pt; }
    
    /* Estilos do layout */
    .wrapper { width: 100%; table-layout: fixed; background-color: #C7CDE9; padding: 40px 0; }
    .main-table { width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
    
    /* Mobile */
    @media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
      .main-table { width: 100% !important; border-radius: 0 !important; }
      .content-padding { padding: 30px 20px !important; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body style="margin:0; padding:0; background-color:#C7CDE9;">
  <center class="wrapper">
    <table class="main-table" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
      
      <tr>
        <td style="background-color: #00020A; padding: 25px 40px;">
          <img src="https://static.autodromo.com.br/uploads/af-logo-white.png" alt="AutoForce" width="130" style="display: block;">
        </td>
      </tr>

      <tr>
        <td style="line-height: 0;">
          <img src="https://static.autodromo.com.br/uploads/2c4a3509-93c5-41d6-ab2d-ed4695de5fba_baixados-1.webp" alt="Sua operação em conformidade com o Guide Renault 2026" width="600" style="width: 100%; max-width: 600px; display: block;">
        </td>
      </tr>

      <tr>
        <td class="content-padding" style="padding: 45px 40px; background-color: #ffffff;">
          <p style="margin: 0 0 20px 0; font-size: 18px; color: #00020A; font-weight: 700;">Olá, Champion!</p>
          
          <p style="margin: 0 0 25px 0; font-size: 16px; color: #4E5265; line-height: 1.6;">
            A <strong>AutoForce</strong> concluiu a atualização do Tema Renault no Autódromo, garantindo conformidade com o <strong>Guide Digital 2026</strong>. Sua concessionária já está preparada para as auditorias de Maio.
          </p>

          <table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
            <tr>
              <td style="border-radius: 6px; background-color: #FF8C00;">
                <a href="https://autoforce.com" target="_blank" style="padding: 14px 28px; font-size: 15px; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; border-radius: 6px;">
                  Confira os próximos passos <span style="font-size: 18px;">↘</span>
                </a>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>

      <tr>
        <td style="background-color: #00020A; padding: 30px; text-align: center;">
          <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 12px; color: #ffffff; opacity: 0.8; letter-spacing: 1px;">
            © 2026 AUTOFORCE
          </p>
        </td>
      </tr>

    </table>
  </center>
</body>
</html>
